# SavdoAI Web Frontend — Environment Variables
# Backend API public origin (no trailing slash). Required for all API calls.
# Local: http://localhost:8000
# Railway: copy the **FastAPI** service’s public HTTPS URL (Settings → Networking; origin only, no /PORT path).
# Do NOT use the Telegram bot worker URL (e.g. hostname savdoai-production.up.railway.app). Live FastAPI example: https://web-production-30ebb.up.railway.app
# Service names differ per project (IaC may use "savdoai" for API; live may use "web" for API) — always pick the URL of the service that runs services/api.
# This variable is read at **build time** (next build / Docker builder stage), not only at container runtime.
NEXT_PUBLIC_API_URL=https://YOUR-FASTAPI-SERVICE.up.railway.app
